                  <h3 id="stoqflow-account-registration">1. StoqFlow Account Registration</h3>
                  <p>You must provide accurate personal and business information during registration and keep that information current. We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account if you provide incomplete, misleading, or false information. You are responsible for all activity on your account.</p>
                  <p>You must open an account with us (a "StoqFlow Account") to use the Services. During registration, we may ask for your name, business details, contact information, branch information, and other relevant details. You must provide accurate and complete information in response to our questions, and you must keep that information current. You are fully responsible for all activity that occurs under your StoqFlow Account, including any actions taken by persons to whom you have granted access. We reserve the right to change the account type, suspend, or terminate any StoqFlow Account that contains inaccurate, untrue, or incomplete information, or that fails to comply with these Terms.</p>

                  <h3 id="restrictions">2. Restrictions</h3>
                  <p>To use our Services, you must refrain from prohibited, abusive, unlawful, or harmful activities. If we reasonably suspect misuse, we may suspend access and, where legally required or permitted, share relevant information with law enforcement or regulatory authorities.</p>
                  <p>You may not, nor may you permit any third party, directly or indirectly, to:</p>
