                    <li>Use the Services for any illegal activity, unlawful goods, fraudulent conduct, or in any way that exposes you, other StoqFlow users, RomanSofts, or our partners to harm.</li>
                    <li>Otherwise use the Services except as expressly allowed under these Terms.</li>
                  </ol>
                  <p>If we reasonably suspect that your StoqFlow Account has been used for an unauthorized, illegal, or criminal purpose, you authorize us to share information about you, your StoqFlow Account, and related transactions with law enforcement or regulatory authorities where appropriate.</p>

                  <h3 id="your-content">3. Your Content</h3>
                  <p>You retain rights to content you upload into the Services, but you grant us the rights reasonably necessary to host, process, display, back up, and use that content within the operation of StoqFlow.</p>
                  <p>The Services may include functionality for uploading or providing suggestions, recommendations, feedback, stories, photos, documents, logos, products, promotions, advertisements, and other materials or information ("Content"). Anything you provide to us or make available through the Services must not contain anything unlawful, obscene, hateful, infringing, deceptive, or harmful to you, our customers, or us. We reserve the right to remove Content at any time where necessary to protect the Services, users, or our legal obligations.</p>

                  <h3 id="security">4. Security</h3>
                  <p>We take security seriously, but no service can guarantee complete protection from unauthorized access. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your password, controlling who has access to your account, and notifying us immediately if you suspect unauthorized use of your account. In the event of a dispute regarding account ownership, we will act as the final decision-maker based on the information reasonably available to us.</p>

                  <h3 id="privacy">5. Privacy</h3>
                  <p>By using any of the Services as a StoqFlow user, you acknowledge our data practices applicable to your use of the platform. We process information needed to operate the Services, support your account, improve performance, and meet legal and regulatory obligations.</p>

                  <h3 id="taxes">6. Taxes</h3>
                  <p>Your taxes are your responsibility. You are responsible for determining any taxes assessed, incurred, or required to be collected, paid, or withheld in relation to your use of the Services. You are also solely responsible for collecting, withholding, reporting, and remitting the correct taxes to the appropriate tax authority. We are not obligated to determine whether taxes apply, or to calculate, collect, report, or remit any taxes arising from your transactions unless expressly stated otherwise in writing.</p>

